<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Formular Feedback – Revizie Tehnică</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg: #D0C9BD;
    --surface: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #1A1A1A;
    --ink-muted: #6B6760;
    --accent: #2D5BE3;
    --accent-light: #EEF2FD;
    --border: #C4BDB1;
    --success: #1A7A4A;
    --success-light: #EDFAF3;
    --warning: #C84B11;
    --warning-light: #FEF0EA;
    --radius: 12px;
    --shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1B2A 0%, #1B2E4B 40%, #1A3A5C 70%, #0F2744 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 32px 32px 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 240px;
  }
  .header-graphic {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; right: -80px;
    width: 320px; height: 320px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(45,91,227,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: drift 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -60px; left: 30%;
    width: 240px; height: 240px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,180,160,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: drift 11s ease-in-out infinite alternate-reverse;
  }
  @keyframes drift {
    from { transform: translate(0,0); }
    to   { transform: translate(20px,-20px); }
  }
  .header-company {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2px;
  }
  .header-tag {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .header h1 {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .header p {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.56);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .header-meta {
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 22px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .meta-pill {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.40);
  }

  /* ── PROGRESS ── */
  .progress-bar {
    background: #B8B0A4;
    height: 7px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1A7A4A, #2DBF76);
    width: 0%;
    transition: width 0.4s ease;
  }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  .main {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 20px 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  /* ── CATEGORY BLOCK ── */
  .category-block {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(12px);
    animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease forwards;
  }
  .category-block:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.10s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.20s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.30s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .category-block:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.40s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .cat-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 18px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .category-block.active .cat-header {
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
  }
  .cat-num {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-light);
    padding: 3px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .cat-title {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .cat-status { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); white-space: nowrap; }
  .cat-status.done { color: var(--success); font-weight: 600; }

  .cat-body {
    display: none;
    padding: 24px 24px 28px;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .category-block.active .cat-body { display: flex; }

  /* ── QUESTION ── */
  .question-wrap {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.25s ease;
  }
  .question-wrap.visible { display: flex; }

  .q-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .btn-next, .btn-prev {
    padding: 9px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-next { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
  .btn-next:hover { background: #1E47CC; }
  .btn-prev { background: transparent; color: var(--ink-muted); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-prev:hover { border-color: var(--ink-muted); color: var(--ink); }

  .q-label { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.5; }
  .q-label .required { color: var(--warning); margin-left: 3px; }

  /* ── STARS ── */
  .star-group { display: flex; flex-direction: row-reverse; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 4px; }
  .star-group input { display: none; }
  .star-group label { font-size: 30px; cursor: pointer; color: #D4CFC8; transition: color 0.15s, transform 0.15s; line-height: 1; }
  .star-group label:hover,
  .star-group label:hover ~ label,
  .star-group input:checked ~ label { color: #F5A623; }
  .star-group input:checked + label { color: #F5A623; transform: scale(1.15); }
  .star-hint { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-muted); }

  /* ── RADIO ── */
  .options-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .option-item {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    padding: 11px 14px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s; font-size: 14px;
  }
  .option-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-light); }
  .option-item input { display: none; }
  .radio-dot {
    width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid var(--border);
    flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    transition: border-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  .option-item.selected { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-light); }
  .option-item.selected .radio-dot { border-color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent); }
  .option-item.selected .radio-dot::after { content: ''; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: white; }

  /* ── SCALE ── */
  .scale-group { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .scale-btn {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    background: white; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; color: var(--ink-muted);
  }
  .scale-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .scale-btn.active { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: white; }
  .scale-labels { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* ── NPS ── */
  .nps-group { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .nps-btn {
    width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    background: white; font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; color: var(--ink-muted);
  }
  .nps-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .nps-btn.active { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: white; }

  /* ── FOLLOW-UP ── */
  .followup-panel { display: none; padding: 14px 16px; background: var(--warning-light); border: 1px solid #F5C5A8; border-radius: 8px; }
  .followup-panel.visible { display: block; }
  .followup-panel p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--warning); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── INPUTS ── */
  .text-input, .textarea-input {
    width: 100%; padding: 11px 13px; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink); background: white;
    transition: border-color 0.15s; outline: none;
  }
  .text-input:focus, .textarea-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .textarea-input { min-height: 90px; resize: vertical; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── GOOGLE ── */
  .google-section {
    background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--radius); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); text-align: center;
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease 0.42s forwards;
  }
  .google-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .google-section h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .google-section p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 420px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .google-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: #4285F4; color: white;
    padding: 13px 26px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .google-btn:hover { background: #3367D6; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* ── SUBMIT ── */
  .submit-section { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); animation: fadeUp 0.4s ease 0.46s forwards; }
  .submit-btn {
    width: 100%; padding: 18px; background: var(--ink); color: white; border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover { background: #2D5BE3; transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .submit-note { text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); margin-top: 10px; }

  /* ── SUCCESS ── */
  .success-screen { display: none; text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .success-screen.visible { display: block; }
  .success-icon { width: 72px; height: 72px; background: var(--success-light); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 24px; font-size: 32px; }
  .success-screen h2 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .success-screen p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cat-body { padding: 18px 16px 22px; }
    .scale-btn { width: 42px; height: 42px; font-size: 14px; }
    .nps-btn { width: 38px; height: 38px; font-size: 13px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <svg class="header-graphic" viewBox="0 0 800 260" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <line x1="0" y1="65" x2="800" y2="65" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.04" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="0" y1="140" x2="800" y2="140" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.04" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="0" y1="215" x2="800" y2="215" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.04" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="160" y1="0" x2="160" y2="260" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="320" y1="0" x2="320" y2="260" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="480" y1="0" x2="480" y2="260" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="640" y1="0" x2="640" y2="260" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="690" cy="50" r="100" fill="none" stroke="#2D5BE3" stroke-opacity="0.14" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <circle cx="690" cy="50" r="62" fill="none" stroke="#2D5BE3" stroke-opacity="0.09" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="690" cy="50" r="26" fill="#2D5BE3" fill-opacity="0.08"/>
    <polygon points="575,210 640,105 705,210" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.06" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="400" y1="0" x2="760" y2="260" stroke="#00B4A0" stroke-opacity="0.07" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="490" y1="0" x2="120" y2="260" stroke="#2D5BE3" stroke-opacity="0.06" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="320" cy="85" r="3" fill="#00B4A0" fill-opacity="0.28"/>
    <circle cx="480" cy="195" r="2" fill="#2D5BE3" fill-opacity="0.32"/>
    <circle cx="600" cy="145" r="2.5" fill="white" fill-opacity="0.12"/>
  </svg>
  <div class="header-company">WinDoors Automatic</div>
  <div class="header-tag">Servicii de mentenanță</div>
  <h1>Cum a decurs revizia?</h1>
  <p>Mulțumim că ați ales serviciile noastre. Feedback-ul dvs. ne ajută să menținem standardele echipei și să îmbunătățim experiența fiecărui client. Vă rugăm să răspundeți sincer — toate răspunsurile sunt confidențiale.</p>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <div class="meta-pill"><span>⏱</span> 5–7 minute</div>
    <div class="meta-pill"><span>🔒</span> Confidențial</div>
    <div class="meta-pill"><span>📋</span> 6 secțiuni</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div></div>

<div class="main" id="formMain">

  <!-- CAT 1 -->
  <div class="category-block active" id="cat-1">
    <div class="cat-header">
      <div class="cat-num">01</div>
      <div class="cat-title">Programare & Timpii de reacție</div>
      <div class="cat-status" id="status-1">0 / 2</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-body">
      <div class="question-wrap visible" id="q-1-1">
        <div class="q-label">1.1. Cât de ușor a fost să programați revizia?<span class="required">*</span></div>
        <div class="star-group" id="q11">
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-5" value="5"><label for="q11-5">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-4" value="4"><label for="q11-4">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-3" value="3"><label for="q11-3">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-2" value="2"><label for="q11-2">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-1" value="1"><label for="q11-1">★</label>
        </div>
        <div class="star-hint">1 = Foarte dificil &nbsp;·&nbsp; 5 = Foarte ușor</div>
        <div class="q-nav"><button class="btn-next" onclick="nextQ(1,1)">Următoarea →</button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="question-wrap" id="q-1-2">
        <div class="q-label">1.2. Echipa a sosit la ora stabilită?<span class="required">*</span></div>
        <div class="options-list">
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="La timp exact"><span class="radio-dot"></span>La timp exact</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Întârziere mică (sub 15 min)"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Întârziere mică (sub 15 min)</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Întârziere semnificativă (15–60 min)"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Întârziere semnificativă (15–60 min)</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Întârziere majoră (peste 60 min)"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Întârziere majoră (peste 60 min)</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Nu au sosit / reprogramat fără preaviz"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Nu au sosit / reprogramat fără preaviz</label>
        </div>
        <div class="q-nav">
          <button class="btn-prev" onclick="prevQ(1,2)">← Înapoi</button>
          <button class="btn-next" onclick="nextQ(1,2)">Următoarea →</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="question-wrap" id="q-1-3">
        <div class="q-label">1.3. Ați fost anunțat în avans în cazul unei întârzieri?</div>
        <div class="options-list">
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q13" value="Da"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Da</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q13" value="Nu"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Nu</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q13" value="Nu a fost cazul"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Nu a fost cazul</label>
        </div>
        <div class="q-nav">
          <button class="btn-prev" onclick="prevQ(1,3)">← Înapoi</button>
          <button class="btn-next" onclick="finishCat(1,2)">Finalizează secțiunea ✓</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CAT 2 -->
  <div class="category-block" id="cat-2">
    <div class="cat-header">
      <div class="cat-num">02</div>
      <div class="cat-title">Durata & Eficiența lucrării</div>
      <div class="cat-status" id="status-2">0 / 2</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-body">
      <div class="question-wrap visible" id="q-2-1">
        <div class="q-label">2.1. Durata reviziei a corespuns cu estimarea comunicată inițial?<span class="required">*</span></div>
        <div class="options-list">
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Da, conform estimării"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Da, conform estimării</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Mai scurtă decât estimat"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Mai scurtă decât estimat</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Ușor mai lungă, cu explicație"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Ușor mai lungă, cu explicație clară</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Semnificativ mai lungă, fără explicație"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Semnificativ mai lungă, fără explicație</label>
        </div>
        <div class="q-nav"><button class="btn-next" onclick="nextQ(2,1)">Următoarea →</button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="question-wrap" id="q-2-2">
        <div class="q-label">2.2. Echipa a lucrat organizat și eficient pe parcursul reviziei?<span class="required">*</span></div>
        <div class="scale-group">
          <button type="button" class="scale-btn" data-q="q22" data-val="1">1</button>
          <button type="button" class="scale-btn" data-q="q22" data-val="2">2</button>
          <button type="button" class="scale-btn" data-q="q22" data-val="3">3</button>
          <button type="button" class="scale-btn" data-q="q22" data-val="4">4</button>
          <button type="button" class="scale-btn" data-q="q22" data-val="5">5</button>
        </div>
        <div class="scale-labels"><span>Deloc organizat</span><span>Complet eficient</span></div>
        <div class="q-nav">
          <button class="btn-prev" onclick="prevQ(2,2)">← Înapoi</button>
          <button class="btn-next" onclick="nextQ(2,2)">Următoarea →</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="question-wrap" id="q-2-3">
        <div class="q-label">2.3. Au existat întreruperi, reveniri sau lucruri refăcute în timpul reviziei?</div>
        <div class="options-list">
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q23" value="Nu"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Nu</label>
          <label class="option-item"><input type="radio" name="q23" value="Da"><span class="radio-dot"></span>Da</label>
        </div>
        <div class="followup-panel" id="q23-followup">
